data.title: Tokheim速 Suction Pump, Single Product/Single Hose
data.meta_description: PMP 25100, OEM 048393, 405952-39, 048740, 405952-6, 048222, 035443. Tokheim速 Suction Pump, Single Product/Single Hose
data.text:
Tokheim Suction Pumping Unit, Single Product, typically Single Hose, one pump in cabinet. For use with 1/3 and 1/2 hp motors.

Used in Tokheim standard flow pump models 162, 262, 785, 1248A, 1248AS, 1250A, 1250AS, all TCS, and some late 1150's.

Used in Gasboy速 pump models 250, xx52, xx52A, xx52TW1, 9122, 9124, and 9822. For 9122, 9124, and 9822, specify "Top Outlet" when ordering.

Note that model xx52TW1 is a single product, two hose configuration, with a 1/2 hp motor. If your xx52TW1 is equipped with a 3/4 hp motor, you may use PMP# 25101 instead of 25100.
